rows.label: qst005803_msg0001
rows.name:
All this digging, and still not a single
sign of anything...

rows.label: qst005803_msg0002
rows.name:
Was there really ever a kingdom
here in Liberalitas?

rows.label: qst005803_msg0003
rows.name: It is a bit of a cramped place for one.

rows.label: qst005803_msg0004
rows.name:
Perhaps the bulk of this kingdom has
sunk into the Cloud Sea. If so, it may
be impossible for anyone to find.

rows.label: qst005803_msg0005
rows.name: ...I have it. I see it all now!

rows.label: qst005803_msg0007
rows.name:
The information that book provided
was nothing but a pack of lies!

rows.label: qst005803_msg0009
rows.name:
Tora and friends played for fools
by lying book?!

rows.label: qst005803_msg0010
rows.name:
Though it pains me to admit it,
it is the only explanation.

rows.label: qst005803_msg0011
rows.name:
I was a fool to come all this way with
no proof that the writings were true.

rows.label: qst005803_msg0012
rows.name:
But there is no use in worrying
about that which is past!

rows.label: qst005803_msg0013
rows.name:
We must cast this failure aside
and seek a different clue!
